A growing collection of notes on data engineering, software engineering, computer science, and related technical subjects.

This project is a personal study notebook and reference library for interview preparation, concept review, and long-term learning.

> **Work in progress**  
> This is an evolving collection based on my knowledge and interests. Some topics are still incomplete or not yet covered.

## Inside this notebook

Topics include:

- computer science fundamentals
- databases and data engineering
- software design and architecture
- system design
- DevOps and CI/CD
- cloud certifications
- data visualization
- OSINT
- deep web technologies

## How to use it

The content is organized by topic, so it can be read either as a reference or as a study guide.

Some notes are brief summaries, while others go deeper into concepts, patterns, and trade-offs.
